room_title: Escape room "Captain's Cove" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: I was really impressed with this room. Puzzles stayed true to the theme, and were often clever. I highly recommend this one!

room_title: Escape room "Captain's Cove" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: We did the pirate one. Loved the decorations and the clues. We were so close to solving it too! Can't wait to do it again.

room_title: Escape room "Captain's Cove" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: We had lots of fun getting out of Captain's Cove. Family friendly room, a little dark for these old eyes but totally enjoyable.

room_title: Escape room "Captain's Cove" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: Had a great time with Captain's Cove. Best of the three escape room locations I've tried in Madison. Will definitely be back.
